ROCK
v.
EXECUTIVE OFFICE PARK OF DURHAM ASSOCIATION, INC. 428P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 15, 2017 Martin E. Rock, for Rock, Martin E. J. Matthew Waters, Attorney at Law, Hope Derby Carmichael, Attorney at Law, Raleigh, for Executive Office Park of Durham Association, Inc.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th of December 2017 by Petitioner to Dismiss Petition for Writ of Certiorari:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 15th of December 2017."
